    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 8. 1 – 3, Spermathecae of Amblyseius acalyphus with none (1), one (2) and three (3) spermatophores. 4 – 8, Amblyseius atlanticus n. sp. female: 4. Dorsal idiosoma, 5. Ventral idiosoma, 6. Spermatheca, 7. Chelicera, 8. Genu, tibia and tarsus of leg IV." ;
